Package: picard
Type: Package
Title: RWE Pipelining Tool
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Martin", "Lavallee", , "martin.lavallee@boehringer-ingelheim.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: A pipeline tool for RWE analysis (typically using the OHDSI stack) that allows users to easily create and run pipelines of R code.
    This package initializes a standard directory structure, builds cohorts, and executes R scripts in a specified order.
